{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3909a247c1","title":"力争和平准备再战","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fcf4f1bbfd","index":0,"year":1946,"month":6,"day":13,"articleId":"3909a247c1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"840282ea99","type":"paragraph","text":"力争和平准备再战”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"3909a247c1"},{"id":"1cd2fa7863","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年6月13日）烧，林、彭，周，叶：（一）我党方针是竭力争取和平，争取于十五天内保持平静，争取延长停战时间，变暂时停战为长期停战。（二）同时我东北全军应积极准备再战，并应准备长期战争。（三）望根据以上基本方针进行工作。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"3909a247c1"},{"id":"ea972b390d","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"3909a247c1"},{"id":"c48fe37cd0","type":"paragraph","text":"已元[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的给北平军事调处执行部第二十七小组沈阳）中共方面负责人饶石，东北民主联军总司令林起、第一政治委员彭","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"3909a247c1"}],"page":{"id":"3946a57bfc","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"3909a247c1","start":387,"end":387}}}},"__N_SSG":true}